# Git Guide for Quick Play

```javascript
$ git add --all
$ git commit -m "<message>"
$ git push origin master
```

```javascript
$ git init
```

```javascript
$ git remote -v
$ git remote add origin <url>
$ git clone <clone>
```

```javascript
$ git branch
$ git branch <name>
$ git checkout <name>
$ git checkout -b <name>
```

```javascript
$ git merge
```

```javascript
$ git pull origin
```

```javascript
$ git status
$ git diff --stat
```

